text: RamblingThis year  Fuck this year  Life does this thing to me where it dangles what I want most right in front of my face and then just when it s within my reach it s snatched away from me and I thrown back into the same cycle of hating my life and telling myself that it ll get better eventually  Guess what  It doesn t get better  Ever  Existence is suffering  There is no good and evil  There is no morality  There is no love  All these things that we are supposed to believe in are simply illusions that keeps us from noticing the pointlessness of life  Love is the reason I m forced to continue this wretched existence  Because my family loves me I have to keep existing even though I don t want to  Every second that I m alive is a struggle  The only things that distract me from the truth are drugs and porn  Things that provide a momentary release from the void  This is my reality  This is what life will be until I die  Hope and love are demons too  we just don t realize
summary: This year is the worst year for me. I hate my life. I have to keep existing even though I don't want to. The only things that distract me from the truth are drugs and porn. Hope and love are demons too.
